  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The trial is conducted in Europe and Middle East. The aim of the trial is to compare the use
      of Insulin Detemir once or twice daily combined with mealtime Insulin Aspart against that of
      NPH Insulin once or twice daily combined with mealtime Insulin Aspart. The trial involves
      children and adolescents with Type 1 Diabetes.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
